    "title": "Ibada Safi",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "ibada safi",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Tangu mwanzo wa uhusiano wa Mungu na Israeli, aliwapa njia za ibada yao kwake ili iwe ya kumpendeza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:1-Exod40:38\">Kutoka 20–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:1-Lev8:36\">Mambo ya Walawi 1–8</a>). Moja ya malengo makuu ya Bwana kwa watu wake ni kuhakikisha wanamtolea ibada safi.</p><p>Wakati Mfalme Solomoni alijenga hekalu kama mahali pa kudumu pa ibada, aliliunda kwa uangalifu &quot;nyumba kwa ajili ya Jina la BWANA Mungu wangu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:3-1Kgs5:5\">1 Wafalme 5:3–5</a>). Alifuata muundo uliotolewa, akaweka Sanduku la Agano katika patakatifu pa ndani, na akalitolea hekalu kwa Bwana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:1-1Kgs8:11\">8:1–11</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:13-Deut16:17\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 16:13–17</a>). Solomoni alitii kanuni za sheria (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:10-Exod25:22\">Kutoka 25:10–22</a>). Kanuni hizi zililenga kuweka ibada ya Israeli ikilenga kwa Bwana na amri zake.</p><p>Watu mara nyingi huabudu kulingana na tamaa zao wenyewe badala ya kufuata maagizo ya Mungu. Israeli haikuwa tofauti. Katika miaka yake ya baadaye, Solomoni hakuwa mwaminifu kwa Bwana kwa kuabudu miungu mingine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:4-1Kgs11:8\">1 Wafalme 11:4–8</a>). Baada ya Solomoni kufa, Yeroboamu alianzisha dini pinzani ya kuabudu sanamu katika ufalme wa kaskazini. Alikiuka waziwazi sheria ya Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:9-1Kgs14:10\">14:9–10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:15-1Kgs14:16\">15–16</a>).</p><p>Ibada ya uongo ilikuwa ya kawaida katika ufalme wa kaskazini katika historia yake yote (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:26\">1 Wafalme 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:13\">16:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:25-1Kgs16:26\">25–26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:30-1Kgs16:33\">30–33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:25-1Kgs21:26\">21:25–26</a>). Wakati huo huo, katika ufalme wa kusini wa Yuda, madhabahu za kipagani za kienyeji zilikuwa kikwazo cha kiroho cha mara kwa mara (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:14\">15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:43\">22:43</a>). Wala Yuda wala Israeli hawakuwa waaminifu katika ibada yao kwa Bwana.</p><p>Kuna Mungu mmoja, na watu wake wanapaswa kumwabudu yeye pekee (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:23\">1 Wafalme 8:23</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:7\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:9\">9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4\">6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">Yohana 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">Matendo 4:12</a>). Ibada yetu inapaswa kutoka kwa moyo safi. Tunapaswa kubaki waaminifu kabisa kwa Bwana katika huduma iliyojitolea kwake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:14\">1 Wafalme 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:1\">17:1</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:20\">20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">Zaburi 24:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:10\">Mathayo 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:24\">Yohana 4:24</a>). Katika ibada yetu ya kila siku na kila wiki kwa Mungu, tunapaswa kuhisi uwepo wake, ukileta furaha ya kweli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1 Wafalme 8:56</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1-Ps63:3\">Zaburi 63:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:4\">Wafilipi 4:4</a>).</p><p>Hekalu la Israeli lilikuwa patakatifu lililokusudiwa kuvutia watu wote kuabudu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:41-1Kgs8:43\">1 Wafalme 8:41–43</a>). Vivyo hivyo, Wakristo, ambao ni hekalu la Mungu aliye hai, wanapaswa kuishi kwa njia inayovutia na kuhamasisha wengine kumjua Bwana na kumwabudu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1 Wakorintho 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:16\">Mathayo 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40-Acts2:47\">Matendo 2:40–47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:5\">2 Timotheo 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:12\">1 Petro 2:12</a>). Maisha yetu yote yanapaswa kujumuisha ibada ya kila siku ya Kristo, tukimtambua kama Bwana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1 Petro 3:15</a>). Hatupaswi kuruhusu sanamu yoyote kuchukua nafasi ya Mungu katika maisha yetu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:21\">1 Yohana 5:21</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20\">Mwanzo 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:31\">Kutoka 4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:10-Exod25:22\">25:10–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:1-Lev8:36\">Mambo ya Walawi 1:1–8:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:7-Deut5:9\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 5:7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4-Deut6:9\">6:4–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12\">10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:20\">20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:13-Deut16:17\">16:13–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:1-Deut26:15\">26:1–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:3-1Kgs5:5\">1 Wafalme 5:3–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:6\">Zaburi 24:3–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1-Ps51:19\">51:1–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">Hosea 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:1-Hos14:2\">14:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:6-Mic6:8\">Mika 6:6–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:10\">Mathayo 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:16\">5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:1-Matt6:18\">6:1–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:19-John4:24\">Yohana 4:19–24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:23\">5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40-Acts2:47\">Matendo 2:40–47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">Warumi 12:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1 Wakorintho 3:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1-1Cor14:40\">14:1–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3\">Wafilipi 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:1-Heb10:25\">Waebrania 10:1–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:15\">1 Petro 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:21\">1 Yohana 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:9-Rev5:13\">Ufunuo 5:9–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3\">15:3</a></p>",
